    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering, featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring a fully documented preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile engagement, while the M-Variable differential ensures precise torque distribution. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component remains in showroom condition, preserving the original factory kinematics. This is an investment-grade chassis with flawless paint depth and a pristine interior, representing the zenith of BMW\u2019s longitudinal driving dynamics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
